{"lemma":"حَرْقُ","slug":"حَرْقُ","root":"ح.ر.ق","root_slug":"ح-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَرْقُ","root":"حرق","pos":"V","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7707","n7708","n7709","n7719","n7710"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to burn","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to burn, to hurt, to sting"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to burn, to destroy by fire, to singe, to scorch","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"قَالُوا حَرِّقُوهُ وَٱنْصُرُوا آلِهَتَكُمْ إِنْ كُنْتُمْ فَاعِلِينَ","english":"They said, \"Burn him and support your gods - if you are to act.\""}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَرَقَ (ḥaraqa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"burning, incineration","tags":["uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"burn, scald, scorch, sear, singe","tags":["countable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"spoiler (document, review or comment that discloses the ending or some key surprise or twist in a story)","tags":["Internet","colloquial"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ح ر ق (ḥ r q), to burn.\n\nIntensive of حَرَقَ (ḥaraqa, “to burn”)."},"ipa":["/ħa.ra.qa/","/ħar.ra.qa/","/ħarq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7707","headword_ar":"حَرْقٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraqN","text_ar":"حَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7708","headword_ar":"حُرْقٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  An"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"angry"},{"kind":"text","text":"man. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7709","headword_ar":"حَرَقٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A burning"},{"kind":"text","text":"by means of fire;] a subst. (Mgh, Msb) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_iHoraAqu","text_ar":"الاـِحْرَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) [i. e.] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iHoraAqu Aln~aAri","text_ar":"اـِحْرَاقُ النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) itself; (Msb;) [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fire of a burning house &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariyqN","text_ar":"حَرِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAriqapN","text_ar":"حَارِقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flame of fire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, Th, Mgh, K.) The first is meant in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAl~apu Almuw^omini Haraqu Aln~aAri","text_ar":"ضَالَّةُ المُوْمِنِ حَرَقُ النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The straybeast of the believer is"},{"kind":"text","text":"a cause of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the burning of fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mgh:) or it here signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the flame of fire:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a trad., meaning that if any one takes the stray-beast of a believer to possess it, his doing so will bring him to the flame of the fire [of Hell]. (Az, Mgh, TA.) And hence, (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaraqu $ahaAdapN","text_ar":"الحَرَقُ شَهَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Burning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flame, is"},{"kind":"text","text":"a cause of one's receiving the reward of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"martyrdom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] occurring in another trad. (TA.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Haraqi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"فِى حَرَقِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the fire of God."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqaY A@ll~`hu AlkaAfira fiY HaAriqatihi","text_ar":"اَلْقَى ا@للّٰهُ الكَافِرَ فِى حَارِقَتِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God cast the unbeliever"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into his fire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A burn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mark of burning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, from the beating"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the washer, and whitener, and the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and so, sometimes, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaroqN","text_ar":"حَرْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hole thus caused in a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, Mgh, TA;) and so, sometimes, ↓ the latter; which also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hole caused by fire, in a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n7719","headword_ar":"حَرَقٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraqN","text_ar":"حَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuroqapN","text_ar":"حُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Heat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some other cause of mischief"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"harm, that burns,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nips, shrinks, shrivels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blasts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuHoriqu","text_ar":"يُحْرِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHoraqN","text_ar":"مُحْرَقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Burnt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Mgh, Msb,) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoruwqN","text_ar":"مَحْرُوقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl. of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaroqaY","text_ar":"حَرْقَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatolaY","text_ar":"قَتْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaroHaY","text_ar":"جَرْحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatiylN","text_ar":"قَتِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariyHN","text_ar":"جَرِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) Thus, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHariyqu $ahiydN","text_ar":"الحَرِيقُ شَهِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The burnt is a martyr"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mgh:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHariqu","text_ar":"الحَرِقُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he who falls into fire, and takes fire and burns."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grating sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the dogtooth by reason of anger, or rage; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuruwqN","text_ar":"حُرُوقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n7710","headword_ar":"حَرِقٌ","root":"Hrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A cloud"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lightening vehemently."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sharp;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the quality of burning;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to an iron head or blade of an arrow or a spear or sword &c.; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuraqapN","text_ar":"حُرَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hur~aAqapN","text_ar":"حُرَّاقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAruwqapN","text_ar":"حَارُوقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to swords. (K.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariyqN","text_ar":"حَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqu Al$~aEari","text_ar":"حَرِقُ الشَّعَرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having the hair falling off piecemeal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariqu","text_ar":"حَرِقُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljanaAHi","text_ar":"الجَنَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a similar meaning; (S, TA;) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the feathers of the wing falling off piecemeal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"short in the wing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having it cut off."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riy$N HariqN","text_ar":"رِيشٌ حَرِقٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Feathers falling off,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":552},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and becoming scattered, by degrees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liHoyapN HariqapN","text_ar":"لِحْيَةٌ حَرِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A beard that is shorter upon the chin than upon the two sides of the face."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariqN","text_ar":"حَرِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the extremities much chapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so some say. (TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoruwqN","text_ar":"مَحْرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]}}